I '''Nicolaus Copernicus''' (a misusulat muring Mikołaj Kopernik or Nikolas Koppernigk, [[Toruń]], [[w:Royal Prussia|Royal Prussia]], [[w:Poland|Polonia]] (Poland), [[Febreru 19]], [[1473]] - [[Frombork]], [[w:Royal Prussia|Royal Prussia]], [[w:Poland|Polonia]], [[Mayu 24]], [[1543]]), metung yang [[astronomer]] a [[w:Poland|Polaco]] (Polish).<ref>Tungkul king bangsa nang Copernicus, a pididibatian da reng Aleman (German) ampong Polaco, anti ing mayayakit kareng Wikipediang Polaco ampong Aleman, lilino ya ing kabilian nung lon ta la reng makatuking kataya, a mebanggit king Castilang Wikipedia: "His country was the province of ancient Royal Prussia, composed of his native Torun and Warmia, both components of the Polish state since 1454" - Barbara Bieńkowska: ''The Scientific World of Copernicus on the Occasion of the 500th Anniversary of His Birth 1473-1973'', 1973, p. 137</ref>  Ya ing mumunang [[astronomer]] a migbalangkas king metung a sistemang [[w:heliocentrism|heliocentric]] (makasentru king [[Aldo]]) a minalili king [[Yatu]] antimong sentru ning sikluban (''universe''). Ing kayang makasalesayan a libru, ing ''[[De revolutionibus orbium coelestium]]'' (''On the Revolutions of the Celestial Spheres'', Dikil kareng Pamandurut/Rebolusion da reng Bola king Banua), ing tuturing dang umpisa ning makabayung [[astronomy]], ampo ing pinandit ning pamangising a pigmulan ning [[w:Scientific Revolution|Rebolusion king Siensia]].

